@startuml v3-theme-light-timing
!theme light from ../../../doubleslash/v3

title UML Theme v3 — Light Mode Timing Smoke Test

robust  "Web Browser" as WB
concise "Web User"    as WU
clock   "Clock_1"     as C1 with period 100 pulse 15 offset 10
binary  "Binary"      as B
analog  "Analog"      as A

WB is Initializing
WU is Absent

@WB
0 is idle
+200 is Processing
+100 is Waiting
WB@0 <-> @50 : {50 ms lag}

@WU
0 is Waiting
+500 is ok
@200 <-> @+150 : {150 ms}

@B
100 is high

@A
0 is 0
100 is 3
300 is 1

legend right
  |= Element |= Quelle |
  | Canvas | root |
  | Lifelines / states | global element |
  | Constraint arrows | global arrow |
  | Labels | global arrow (Font*) |
endlegend

footer Smoke test for puml-theme-light.puml (v3 timing)

@enduml
